<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>College Department - SIT Nagpur</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        header p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        nav a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        nav a:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .departments {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .dept-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .dept-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .dept-card h3 {
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Symbiosis Institute of Technology</h1>
            <p>College Department Portal</p>
        </header>
        
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html">Home</a>
            <a href="student-info.html">Student Information</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="content">
            <section class="section">
                <h2>Welcome to SIT Nagpur</h2>
                <p>Symbiosis Institute of Technology (SIT) Nagpur is a premier institution dedicated to fostering academic excellence and innovation in the field of technology and education.</p>
                <p>Our college department offers comprehensive programs designed to equip students with the knowledge and skills necessary for success in the modern world.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="section">
                <h2 id="about">About Our Departments</h2>
                <div class="departments">
                    <div class="dept-card">
                        <h3>Computer Science</h3>
                        <p>Advanced programs in software development, artificial intelligence, and cybersecurity.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dept-card">
                        <h3>Electronics & Telecommunication</h3>
                        <p>Cutting-edge research and development in telecommunications and electronics.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dept-card">
                        <h3>Mechanical Engineering</h3>
                        <p>Comprehensive training in modern mechanical engineering principles and practices.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="section">
                <h2 id="contact">Quick Links</h2>
                <p><strong>For Student Information:</strong> <a href="student-info.html" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: underline;">Click here to view Student Information</a></p>
            </section>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Symbiosis Institute of Technology, Nagpur. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // Display welcome alert
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            alert('Welcome to SIT Nagpur');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
      
